def discounts(table3,j):
    discount = []
    for i in  table3.iloc[:,j]:
    
        try:
            discount.append(float(i[0].split('-')[0])-float(i[0].split('-')[1]))
        except:
            discount.append(0)
    return discount
def discountrate(table3,j):
    discount = []
    for i in  table3.iloc[:,j]:
    
        try:
            discount.append(float(i[0].split('-')[1])/float(i[0].split('-')[0]))
        except:
            discount.append(0)
    return discount

def tableproduct(soup):
    tablex = []
    name = soup.find_all(attrs={"class": "shopguide-info-wrapper"})[0].text
    sorces = [soup.find_all(attrs={'class':'shopguide-info-extra'})[0].find_all('p')[i].text.split() for i in range(5)]
    for i in soup.find_all(attrs={"class": "shopmenu-food ng-isolate-scope"}):
        pname = i.find_all(attrs={'class':'shopmenu-food-name ui-ellipsis ng-binding'})[0].text
        psale = i.find_all(attrs={'class':"color-mute ng-binding"})[1].text
        pprice = i.find_all(attrs={'class':"col-3 shopmenu-food-price color-stress ng-binding"})[0].text
        tablex.append([name,pname,psale,pprice])    
    return tablex,sorces,name
def products(soup):
    pross = []
    name = soup.find_all(attrs={"class": "shopguide-info-wrapper"})[0].text
    for j in soup.find_all(attrs={'class':'commentitem-content'}):
        pross.append([name,[i.text.split()[0] for i in j.find_all(attrs={'class':'shoprate-itemrating shoprate-itemratinglist ng-isolate-scope'})]])
    return pross
# 返回菜单、评分地址、店名
def mainproduct(url):
    result = returnresult(url)
    soup = returnsoup(result)
    pross = products(soup)
    product,sorces,name = tableproduct(soup)
    return product,sorces,name ,pross

def dealproduct(table):
    
    table.iloc[:,2] = [float(i[0]) if i!=[] else np.nan for i in table.iloc[:,2].str.findall('\d+')]
    table.iloc[:,3] = [float(i[0]) if i!=[] else np.nan for i in table.iloc[:,3].str.findall('^[1-9]\d+\.\d+|0\.\d+[1-9]\d+$|\d+')]
   
    table.columns = ['店名','产品','月售','售价']
    return table

def getall(urls):
    shopname = []
    productlist = []
    sorcelist = []
    productss = []
    for  i in urls:
        product,sorces,name ,pross=mainproduct(i)
        shopname.append(name)
        productlist.append(product)
        sorcelist.append(sorces)
        productss.append(pross)
        print('-',end='|')
    return productlist,sorcelist,shopname,productss

直接降价促销的效果可能有限，需要形成重点单品¶

def dealshop(table):
    table.iloc[:,0] = [float(i[0]) if i!=[] else np.nan for i in table.iloc[:,0].str.findall('^[1-9]\d+\.\d+|0\.\d+[1-9]\d+$|\d+')]
    table.iloc[:,1] = [float(i[0]) if i!=[] else np.nan for i in table.iloc[:,1].str.findall('^[1-9]\d+\.\d+|0\.\d+[1-9]\d+$|\d+')]    
    table.iloc[:,2] = [float(i[0]) if i!=[] else np.nan for i in table.iloc[:,2].str.findall('^[1-9]\d+\.\d+|0\.\d+[1-9]\d+$|\d+')]
   
    table.columns = ['综合评价高于周边商家','服务态度','菜品评价','地址','营业时间']
    return table
